products-cosmossql-source

cosmicworks --> products

SELECT 
    p.id, 
    p.categoryId, 
    p.name, 
    p.price,
    p._ts
FROM 
    products p 
WHERE 
    p._ts > @HighWaterMark 
ORDER BY 
    p._ts

Results ordered by _ts

